The definition of `toComplexMeasure` is `ComplexMeasure.mk (fun s => (toBoundedBilin f).integral s) ...`. So the integral of `f` against `E` is `∫ f z dE(z)`.

In our case, `f` is `Function.Embedding.subtype (spectrum ℂ a)`, which is the identity function on `spectrum ℂ a`.

